channel.title: Need help with Aeolian Clientq
channel.description:
I only have one problem.
His spray he put on, can someone tell me how to get it off? I put my picture on and it just goes behind it, you can still see the torches and his silver Aeolian name.
Does anybody know how I can remove his background of the torches and his name? http://img820.imageshack.us/i/54119519.png/
Thanks.

item.title: Need help with Aeolian Clientq
item.dc:creator: @Duke_Nukem Duke Nukem
item.description:
@Duke_Nukem wrote:

[quote=“Imaginary, post:2, topic:352696”]It’s not that hard.
Go to Your Client > Files > Client Files > Cache > Sprites
Then look for the Image that has the spay paint through those pictures + folders and delete it, then compile.
That’s all.
Good luck.[/quote]

I don’t have those files.

Read full topic
